{"tid":533621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"夏威夷澄清誤發導彈警報 鹹網瀏覽量激增","createTime":"2018-01-19T03:33:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T05:04:32.000Z","uid":39464,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5b1c6bcd918a246925f05367e77756771082a180","tid":533621,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T03:33:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180118/large/1516268088_ee6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180118%2Flarge%2F1516268088_ee6d.jpg&h=17c930c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國夏威夷上周六誤發導彈來襲警報，一度引起市民恐慌，其後夏威夷危難管理局澄清只是一次誤警。AV網站Pornhub表示，警報發佈後，來自夏威夷的瀏覽量較正常少77%，但當局澄清屬誤報後，瀏覽量隨即急速上升，較正常高近50%。<br />\n<br />\nPornhub表示，在上午8時07分發佈警報後的20分鐘內，網站流量較正常大幅下跌77%，網站認為因為人們都在努力尋求庇護所，故「無時間瀏覽網站」。直至8時45分，管理局在Twitter上澄清「夏威夷沒有導彈威脅」後16分鐘，網站流量便急速上升，到9時01分時達到高峰，較正常高近50%。<br />\n<br />\n導彈來襲警報令民眾恐懼、壓力上升，不少司機遺下汽車，逃往附近隧道躲藏，有髮廊東主向顧客發短訊，取消所有預約，並表示全日不營業。當大家確認誤報後，可能都需要減壓，而登入AV網站似乎是不少人的「熱門選擇」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180118/57722747\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180118%2F57722747&d=gOWvjm7v2wDT3Waua6LgiMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=33d3fee3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180118%2F57722747&h=4fcf0c35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180118/57722747</a>"},{"pid":"de35cde1ce0e87b95c649b2ba1286403f122cda7","tid":533621,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T03:34:50.000Z","msg":"最後1J"},{"pid":"dd5ce251298bb2371c492d58d2da8b70315bf81b","tid":533621,"uid":133529,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T03:40:40.000Z","msg":"如果發生係香港，D 連登仔絕對會衝上街係咁屌女,，咩欣宜呀，CATGIRL呀個D絕對唔會放過，因為